metadata.name: hedsPLAYER #1
metadata.description: hedsPLAYER is a collection of 333 interactive music players, each with unique art. The audio included, engineered by the heds team, was sourced from multiple artists across the globe using an audio prompt. On any NFT, click a button to start making your own track. Art and music by heds. Built by Secret Garden. Visit https://secretgarden.fm to record and share your own mixes. More information at https://heds.app.
